<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
        <style>
            :root {
                --pastor-card-bg: #ffffff;
                --pastor-accent: var(--color-primary);
            }

            .pastor-hero {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 4rem;
                margin-bottom: 5rem;
                position: relative;
            }

            .pastor-img-wrapper {
                flex: 0 0 320px;
                position: relative;
                z-index: 1;
            }

            .pastor-img-wrapper::before {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                top: 20px;
                left: 20px;
                right: -20px;
                bottom: -20px;
                background: var(--color-bg-alt);
                border-radius: 30px;
                z-index: -1;
                transition: all 0.5s ease;
            }

            .pastor-img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 420px;
                object-fit: cover;
                border-radius: 30px;
                box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
                transition: transform 0.5s ease;
            }

            .pastor-hero:hover .pastor-img {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }

            .pastor-hero:hover .pastor-img-wrapper::before {
                transform: translate(10px, 10px);
                background: rgba(0, 69, 140, 0.05);
            }

            .pastor-info-header {
                flex: 1;
            }

            .pastor-role-badge {
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 8px 20px;
                background: rgba(0, 69, 140, 0.1);
                color: var(--color-primary);
                border-radius: 50px;
                font-weight: 700;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                letter-spacing: 0.1em;
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
                text-transform: uppercase;
            }

            .pastor-name-main {
                font-size: 4rem;
                font-weight: 900;
                color: var(--color-text);
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
                line-height: 1;
                letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            }

            .pastor-name-main span {
                color: var(--color-primary);
            }

            .pastor-intro-text {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
                color: var(--color-text-light);
                line-height: 1.5;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
                max-width: 500px;
            }

            .pastor-message-card {
                background: white;
                padding: 4rem;
                border-radius: 40px;
                box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
                position: relative;
                margin-bottom: 5rem;
                border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            }

            .pastor-message-card::after {
                content: '"';
                position: absolute;
                top: -20px;
                right: 40px;
                font-size: 12rem;
                color: var(--color-primary);
                opacity: 0.05;
                font-family: serif;
                line-height: 1;
            }

            .message-title {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
                font-weight: 800;
                color: var(--color-primary);
                margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 15px;
            }

            .message-title::before {
                content: '';
                width: 40px;
                height: 4px;
                background: var(--color-primary);
                border-radius: 2px;
            }

            .pastor-description-content {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
                line-height: 2.2;
                color: var(--color-text);
                word-break: keep-all;
            }

            .pastor-description-content p {
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            }

            @media (max-width: 992px) {
                .pastor-hero {
                    flex-direction: column;
                    gap: 3rem;
                    text-align: center;
                }

                .pastor-img-wrapper {
                    flex: 0 0 auto;
                    width: 320px;
                    margin: 0 auto;
                }

                .pastor-img {
                    height: 400px;
                }

                .pastor-name-main {
                    font-size: 3rem;
                }

                .pastor-intro-text {
                    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
                }
            }

            @media (max-width: 768px) {
                .pastor-message-card {
                    padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
                    border-radius: 25px;
                }

                .pastor-name-main {
                    font-size: 2.5rem;
                }

                .pastor-description-content {
                    font-size: 1.1rem;
                    line-height: 1.8;
                }

                .message-title {
                    font-size: 1.4rem;
                }
            }
        </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

        <section class="page-header" data-aos="fade">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">섬기는 사람들</h1>
                <ul class="breadcrumb" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <li><a href="/">홈</a></li>
                    <li>교회</li>
                    <li class="active">담임목사</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="container" style="padding-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);">
            <% if (locals.user && user.isAdmin) { %>
                <div style="text-align: right; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
                    <% if (typeof pastor !=='undefined' && pastor.id) { %>
                        <a href="#"
                            onclick="openAdminModal('/admin/edit/pastorProfiles/<%= pastor.id %>', '담임목사 소개 수정')"
                            class="btn btn-primary">프로필 수정하기</a>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <a href="#" onclick="openAdminModal('/admin/write/pastorProfiles', '담임목사 소개 작성')"
                                class="btn btn-primary">프로필 작성하기</a>
                            <% } %>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                    <div style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
                        <!-- Hero Section -->
                        <div class="pastor-hero">
                            <div class="pastor-img-wrapper" data-aos="fade-right">
                                <img src="<%= (typeof pastor !== 'undefined' && pastor.image) ? pastor.image : '/images/pastor.jpg' %>"
                                    class="pastor-img"
                                    alt="<%= typeof pastor !== 'undefined' ? pastor.name : '홍길동' %> 목사님">
                            </div>
                            <div class="pastor-info-header" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="200">
                                <span class="pastor-role-badge">
                                    <%= typeof pastor !=='undefined' ? pastor.role : 'Senior Pastor' %>
                                </span>
                                <h2 class="pastor-name-main">
                                    <%= typeof pastor !=='undefined' ? pastor.name : '김정배' %><span>.</span>
                                </h2>
                                <p class="pastor-intro-text">
                                    하나님의 은혜와 평강이 정배교회 모든 성도님들의 삶속에 함께하시길 기도합니다.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Message Card -->
                        <div class="pastor-message-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                            <div class="message-title">환영의 말씀</div>
                            <div class="pastor-description-content">
                                <%- typeof pastor !=='undefined' ? pastor.description
                                    : '<p>"오직 말씀과 기도로 거룩하여짐이라" (딤전 4:5)</p><p>정배교회를 섬기는 김정배 목사입니다.</p><p>우리 교회는 지역사회를 섬기고, 복음의 기쁨을 함께 나누는 따뜻한 공동체입니다.</p>'
                                    %>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Related Action -->
                        <div class="related-info-section" data-aos="fade-up">
                            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--color-text-light); font-weight: 600;">다른 교회 안내
                                보기</h4>
                            <div class="church-info-links">
                                <a href="/church/philosophy" class="btn btn-outline">교회 소개</a>
                                <a href="/church/history" class="btn btn-outline">교회 연혁</a>
                                <a href="/church/worship" class="btn btn-outline">예배 안내</a>
                                <a href="/church/location" class="btn btn-outline">오시는 길</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
            <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>